{{infobox country at games | NPC = ITA | NPCname = [[Comitato Italiano Paralimpico]] | games = Winter Paralympics | year = 1994 | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = {{url|www.comitatoparalimpico.it }}&nbsp;{{it icon}} | location = [[Lillehammer]] | competitors = 24 | sports = | flagbearer = | rank = 17 | gold = 0 | silver = 7 | bronze = 6 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = 1980 | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = }} '''[[Italy]]''' competed at the '''[[1994 Winter Paralympics]]''' in [[Lillehammer]], [[Norway]]. 24 competitors from Italy won 13 medals, 7 silver and 6 bronze, and finished 17th in the [[1994 Winter Paralympics medal table|medal table]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.paralympic.org/italy|title=Italy - National Paralympic Committee|website=www.paralympic.org|access-date=2016-06-16}}</ref>
